---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 24, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for B2B Solutions — the terms governing use of our website and services."
>
  <Header />

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-blue prose-lg max-w-none
        prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:text-gray-900
        prose-p:text-gray-600 prose-p:leading-relaxed
        prose-a:text-blue-700 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline
        prose-strong:text-gray-900
        prose-ul:text-gray-600 prose-li:leading-relaxed
        prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:mt-10 prose-h2:mb-4
        prose-h3:text-lg prose-h3:mt-6 prose-h3:mb-2">

        <p>These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the B2B Solutions website and services. By accessing our website or engaging our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use our website or services.</p>

        <h2>1. Services</h2>
        <p>B2B Solutions provides professional business support services including bookkeeping, HR solutions, payroll administration, administrative support, document creation, and professional network referrals. Specific terms for individual service engagements will be set forth in a separate service agreement or proposal.</p>

        <h2>2. Use of This Website</h2>
        <p>You agree to use this website only for lawful purposes and in a manner that does not infringe the rights of others. You may not:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the site in any way that violates applicable local, state, national, or international law</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the website or its related systems</li>
          <li>Transmit any unsolicited or unauthorized advertising or promotional material</li>
          <li>Use the site to harm, threaten, or harass any person</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. SMS / Text Message Terms</h2>

        <h3>Program Description</h3>
        <p>B2B Solutions sends SMS messages for client communications (appointment reminders, service follow-ups) and marketing purposes (tips, promotions, service announcements) to users who have opted in.</p>

        <h3>Consent</h3>
        <p>By providing your mobile phone number and opting in — whether through our contact form, booking system, or direct agreement — you consent to receive recurring automated and non-automated text messages from B2B Solutions. Consent is not a condition of purchasing any goods or services.</p>

        <h3>Opting Out</h3>
        <p>Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to any text message to unsubscribe. You will receive one confirmation message and no further texts. Reply <strong>START</strong> at any time to re-subscribe. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for assistance.</p>

        <h3>Costs</h3>
        <p>Message and data rates may apply. Message frequency varies. B2B Solutions is not responsible for charges from your mobile carrier.</p>

        <h3>Supported Carriers</h3>
        <p>Service is available on most major U.S. carriers. Carrier availability may vary and carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</p>

        <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on this website — including text, graphics, logos, and images — is the property of B2B Solutions and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our express written permission.</p>

        <h2>5. Confidentiality</h2>
        <p>In the course of providing services, B2B Solutions may have access to confidential business information. We treat all client information as confidential and do not disclose it to third parties except as required to deliver services or as required by law.</p>

        <h2>6. Disclaimers</h2>
        <p>Our website and its content are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied. B2B Solutions does not warrant that the website will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components.</p>
        <p>The information on this website is for general informational purposes only and does not constitute legal, financial, or professional advice. Consult a qualified professional for advice specific to your situation.</p>

        <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, B2B Solutions shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of our website or services, even if we have been advised of the possibility of such damages.</p>

        <h2>8. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>You agree to indemnify and hold harmless B2B Solutions and its owners, employees, and agents from any claims, damages, or expenses (including reasonable attorneys' fees) arising out of your use of our website or violation of these Terms.</p>

        <h2>9. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Our website links to and integrates with third-party services (including Zoho Forms and Zoho Bookings). Your use of those services is governed by their own terms and privacy policies. We are not responsible for the content or practices of third-party platforms.</p>

        <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Washington, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of our services shall be resolved in the appropriate courts located in Thurston County, Washington.</p>

        <h2>11. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. Continued use of our website or services after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>

        <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about these Terms, please contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@b2bsolutions.biz">info@b2bsolutions.biz</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone (West Coast):</strong> <a href="tel:3605292672">360-529-2672</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone (Midwest):</strong> <a href="tel:3194510501">319-451-0501</a></li>
          <li><strong>Locations:</strong> Rochester, WA &amp; Cedar Rapids, IA</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
